[5E] Sri Lanka
Date: Thu 3 Jun 2021 11:42 p.m. IST
Source: The Daily Mirror [edited]
http://www.dailymirror.lk/breaking_news/COVID-19-death-toll-exceeds-1-600-with-42-deaths/108-213386


Another 42 COVID-19 related deaths were reported, bringing the death toll in the country to 1608, the Government Information Department said. According to the statement issued by the Department, 25 males and 17 females are among the deceased.

